        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="hoverCard text-center shadow p-4">
          <div class="hoverCardIcon">
            <i class="fa fa-paper-plane"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="hoverCardTitle">Custom Links</div>
          <hr>
          <div class="hoverCardBody mt-4">
            Create links that are highly understandeable. Create Unlimited number of Custom links with Clickify and make your customer understand why they should click your link.
          </div>
        </div>
