            <i class="fa fa-heart"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="hoverCardTitle">Free Forever</div>
          <hr>
          <div class="hoverCardBody mt-4">
            Clickify is and will be free for everyone, forever. At Clickify we believe, everyone deserves unlimited free short-links.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div id="pricing" class="call-to-action bg-primary p-5 text-center">
